Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(800,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I can't do it." "It's too frustrating."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Break down those hurdles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is nothing I can't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is being manipulated on the field?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not frightened yet I get told to go away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The path to the unseen future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I may not be able to choose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Close your eyes, and shuffle your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:01:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As promised, yes! you are the winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never lose! Shuffle your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ever since that miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.18,0:01:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wyvern Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Kuriboh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuriboh is shielded by the Hexagram Curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so what of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter whether I play a Monster or {\i1}not{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I need to do is drain your Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...eat {\i1}this{\i0} once again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,FIREBALL!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,""Take It Back! The Red-Eyes Black Dragon\N of Friendship"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NO!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YUGI!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My deck's been powered up {\i1}way too much{\i0} with these banned cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even {\i1}need{\i0} Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't you feel pain in your Duelist's heart...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Duelist's heart?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know what you're talkin' about!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain I'm feeling right now isn't from the burning sensation of your {\i1}cards{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the pain of my {\i1}sadness{\i0} seeing you lose your heart as a Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless no matter how much you scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:03:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've implanted Jounouchi with the memory of my hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's become my loyal puppet, living only for the sole purpose of killing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will {\i1}crush{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}you{\i0}r turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do I have to do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do I have to do get your heart back, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! Wake up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other... me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've felt you hurt this much...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can cut that pain in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let {\i1}me{\i0} fight Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, when I was afraid of everyone, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} called me his best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Jounouchi-kun risked his own life to save me from that fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s always helping me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this time it's {\i1}my{\i0} turn...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... this Duel is too difficult!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you once told me this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That it wasn't the power of the Millennium Puzzle that allowed me to make friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I made it come true on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to {\i1}prove{\i0} that in this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can get back Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I really will make a wish come true on my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then feel... I can say that {\i1}proudly{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I ever feel your life is in serious danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking over that very instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun, {\i1}I'll{\i0} be your opponent now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Yugi's vessel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's{\i0} going to fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A vessel's nothing more than a mere {\i1}vessel{\i0} and {\i1}nothing{\i0} more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just destroying the vessel....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I beat the hateful Pharaoh face-to-face, I won't be able to satisfy my grudge!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Forget it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I beat his vessel to a bloody pulp, there's no way he'll be able to just sit and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kill Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crush him! {\b0}Crush{\b1} him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And drag the Pharaoh out once {\b0}more{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner! There's only one card
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}sleeping in this deck that holds the ability to awaken Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I better draw that card!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Red-Eyes Black Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}san{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got no choice...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}, stay right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna get outta this in one piece, you better do as we tell ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keh! Aren't {\i1}you{\i0} guys cocky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can beat these guys, but Shizuka-{\i0}chan{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your filthy hands off Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you people doing huddling together like this during the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell're {\i1}you{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Ryuji Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Grab the girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get outta here, Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who {\i1}are{\i0} those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let em get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After them!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Red-Eyes Black Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s Duelist's heart dwells within that card!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The card Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} fought with for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything depends on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crush him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crush him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crush them {\b0}both{\b1}, Jounouchi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get your heart back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To prove our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please, red-eyed dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:08:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Speak to Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} with your soul and awaken his Duelist's heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come {\i1}on{\i0} already!\N What are you {\i1}waiting{\i0} for, Yugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn, ya know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have two Monsters on the field... Kuriboh and the 2600 Defense Power Big Shield Gardna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I sacrifice these two Monsters, I can Summon the Red-Eyes Black Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We only have 1300 Life Points left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Proceed with caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a Death Duel where the player whose Life hits 0 loses their life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't find a way to settle this and save both my partner and Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hurry the hell up, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Five cards in my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's something I want to make sure of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}before I play the Red-Eyes this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... if it doesn't work, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How will you get out of this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's about time you show me what you've got planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi's expression changed this turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did he switch places with our usual Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to get Jounouchi's heart back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please, {\b0}both{\b1} Yugis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get Jounouchi back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta remember, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the "circle of friendship" we made together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look! This is the proof of our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's... this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The magic marker ink will eventually fade away...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but our hearts and our friendship will never disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bond of friendship we swore then hasn't disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anzu's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The vow of friendship we swore then should still be in our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm certain it's in Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... {\b0}believe{\b1} in Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other me, I'd like for you to not say anything and just watch what I'm about to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exchange!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Exchange"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A card that allows you to exchange cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, what the hell are you playing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it your hand must really suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I {\i1}must{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you only got junky cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red-Eyes...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take whichever card you want out of these five cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew the vessel was inexperienced as a Duelist,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I never imagined he was {\i1}this{\i0} bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving us his rare card just like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi! The Red-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take the Red-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn {\i1}right{\i0} I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got nothing to be afraid of if I have {\i1}this{\i0} card!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my Red-Eyes back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It really didn't work...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he takes the Red-Eyes, we won't be able to get Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s heart back...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why can't I take it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take that Red-Eyes Black Dragon, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You didn't take the Red-Eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't {\i1}need{\i0} Monster Cards to beat you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My player-damaging banned Magic Cards are more than enough to crush Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to draw a card from your hand now too, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know for sure now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you haven't lost your true Duelist's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:13:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You swore to battle me in Battle City with your pride on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you swore not to use the Red-Eyes Black Dragon until that time came.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you couldn't take the Red-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}told{\i0} you to shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a load of {\i1}crap{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I confirmed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this Red-Eyes card, I can call back your heart as a Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before you try that shit against me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring your Life Points to 0 and sink you into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll always be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna use your card now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrifice two Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Summon the Red-Eyes Black Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Red-Eyes... Black... Dragon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you choose the Red-Eyes like I {\i1}told{\i0} you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he breaking free of my spell over him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or was Yugi's pathetic blabbering stronger than my ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Malik.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that Yugi's friends have gotten away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come and report that to me {\i1}personally{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'll forgive your failure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry the hell up and {\i1}bring them to me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red-Eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sharing a rareness almost equivalent to my Blue-Eyes... Red-Eyes Black Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That used to be Jounouchi's rarest card...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's trying to use that Red-Eyes to get Jounouchi's heart back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But will it {\i1}work{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}, you should see the color of sadness died in the Red-Eyes' eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red-Eyes wants to get your Duelist's heart back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To do that, we'll fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red-Eyes, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Mega Flare!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}! I have faith in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the {\i1}hell{\i0} are you doing, Jounouchi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That attack was {\i1}nothin'{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm gonna use my illegal Magic Cards to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}finished{\i0}, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crush him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\b0}Crush{\b1} him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\b0}CRUSH{\b1} HIM!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner, it's getting too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll take it from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me fight 'till the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I solved the Millennium Puzzle, I wished for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I met you within my heart, I learned to have courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I made important friends too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... somewhere inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I think that if I hadn't met you, I would've stayed a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still feel that way sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I have to get Jounouchi-kun's heart back in this Duel with my {\i1}own{\i0} strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\u1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I ask you to just watch, my other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But this is an incredibly dangerous fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and you could die if you make the slightest mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll trust Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} until the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you insist on going that far, I'll back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't let yourself die, other me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.13,0:17:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mhm-hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, other me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I keep the Millennium Puzzle away from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my other self can't switch minds with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! How long are you gonna {\i1}stand{\i0} there for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've always protected me up until now, other me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I don't get stronger, you'll never be able to leave me heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have plenty of time to think when you're {\i1}dead{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From here on, this is {\b0}my{\b1} battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes! My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't {\i1}need{\i0} Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireball!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Directly attack the player!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They ain't here, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Those guys sure are fast at running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find em!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:17:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search the entire vicinity!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we dodged them for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should hide out here for a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But really, you sure saved my butt, Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I thought you were in America contracting Dungeon Dice Monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just returned to Japan briefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about the Battle City tournament being held here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I'd meet Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0} in all this commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's going on here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl's Jounouchi's sister named Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}kidding{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} had a sister {\i1}that{\i0} cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0} here you say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So who were those guys back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were they after you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're with a gang of thugs called the Ghouls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're a filthy group that steals cards from Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:19:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, they're also known as the Rare Hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard countless rumors about these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm betting they're after Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have no clue why they want {\i1}us{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even {\i1}have{\i0} any rare cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So my big brother's in danger as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're after us, then Anzu and Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come {\i1}on{\i0}! What's {\i1}wrong{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}way{\i0} too early to be on your knees!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Just stop this already, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} and Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there! Hurry and stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we try, Anzu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he activates that switch,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the container above Anzu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These {\i1}scum{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just... can't bring your Life Points to 0 after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:20:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... I'd like for you to just hear my wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn ain't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Rocket Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any Monster this guy attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has their Attack reduced to 0 for the duration of the turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then play the Magic Card Attrition!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take this precious puzzle of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my Battle Phase!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transform into your Invincible Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the Red-Eyes!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want the Millennium Puzzle to sink into the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Permanent Magic, Attrition!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate it's Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It receives damage equal to the difference of the attacking Monster's Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How {\i1}'bout{\i0} it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when the time comes, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It hurts...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell is this pain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you... to keep my Millennium Puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my place...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(139,144)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi gives Jounouchi the Millennium Puzzle to keep it from sinking into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That still isn't enough to stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Malik's control over him seems to be weakening!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi has started to disobey his orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's hardly any time left before the time bomb goes off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:21:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they don't finish their Duel in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:22:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll both fall into the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Countdown to Despair"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.38,0:22:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel like I've been here, been in this place before
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.81,0:22:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the classroom shaded by the setting sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.23,0:22:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I laughed along and pointed with my too shortly cut bangs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Little by little, time keeps going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:23:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My bangs now over my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.80,0:23:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sunset took everyone together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.01,0:23:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure nothing changed while we were there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I kept on searching for something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.61,0:23:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you understood such a senseless time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.78,0:23:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was the answer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.50,0:23:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From here, always...
